Enrique Diosdado https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Enrique_Diosdado 0 Enrique Diosdado (May 6, 1910 – December 1, 1983) was a Spanish actor. He is sometimes credited as Enrique Alvarez Diosdado. Diosdado was a leading man of Argentine and Spanish films of the 1940s and 1950s. His daughter, Ana Diosdado, was a leading Spanish writer and playwright. His son, also named Enrique Álvarez-Diosdado, worked as a director and writer for several tv documentary series and films. Enrique_Diosdado ( May_6_,_1910 – December_1_,_1983 ) was a_Spanish_actor .
